title: dryadinteract
body:
What do you want?
[[Got any tips for me?|dryadhelp]][[I just want to chat|dryadchat]][[Who are you?|dryadinfo]][[Nothing|Leave]]

title: dryadinfo
body:
I'm a Dryad, a female tree spirit...
Can't you tell I'm a woman by my girlish figure?
ENTs are much scarier than us!
They are truly monstrous...
But our only option I guess...
Thank Gaia for sexual dimorphism
[[Whatever you say...|dryadinfoend]][[ENTs much be desperate...|dryadinfoend]]

title: Leave
body:
Until next time...
If you survive until next time that is...
[[That's cheerful...|dryadgoodbye]] [[I'll try...|dryadgoodbye]]

title: dryadchat1
body:
I think I saw a vampire go through one of those doors earlier...
You HAVE to tell me if you see one!
Vampires are so dreamy...
[[Sure if you don't have blood...|dryadchatend]][[Maybe if it's Brad Pitt...|dryadchatend]]

title: dryadhelp1
body:
Maybe you should try going through one of those doors...
Watch out for other trees though!
They aren't all as nice and beautiful as I am...
[[Sure...|dryadhelpend]][[I'll try...|dryadhelpend]]

title: dryadhelp2
body:
Be wary of pregnant women...
Have you ever seen one of them angry?
*shudder*
I'm so glad Dryads don't get pregnant like humans...
I would never do that to my body!
[[I think it's amazing our bodies can do that|dryadhelpend]][[I agree,pregnancy is terrifying!|dryadhelpend]]

title: dryadhelp3
body:
Watch out for women who dress in skimpy clothing...
They always attract danger...
[[That does seem to be true...|dryadhelpend]] [[Wow...slut shame much?|dryadhelpend]]

title: dryadchat2
body:
You'd be surprised at how old I am...
I know older women are only supposed to be wise if we look our age...
But I am very wise even if my bark is flawless...
[[Yes, you do look lovely|dryadchatend]][[Hmmmm...|dryadchatend]]

title: dryadchat3
body:
Letting men do boring jobs makes things so much easier don't you think?
This way I can focus on my bark-care routine...
Being beautiful is much more important than making rules!
[[I suppose...|dryadchatend]][[Are you serious right now?|dryadchatend]]

title: dryadchat4
body:
I know you didn't ask for advice, but you'd better put on some more clothes...
You wouldn't want men to get the wrong impression...
They might hurt you...
[[I'll get right on that...|dryadchatend]] [[Maybe men should control themselves...|dryadchatend]]

title: dryadchat5
body:
Go away!
I am primping my leaves for a date with this fearsome ENT who asked me out...
[[Good luck!|dryadchatend]] [[Hmmmm...|dryadchatend]]
